pesticide.PPE: Applicators and other handlers must wear: Long-sleeved shirt and long pants; Chemical-resistant gloves; Shoes plus socks; Mixers and loaders must wear a chemical-resistant apron in addition to other PPE. Discard clothing and other absorbent materials that have been drenched or heavily contaminated with this product’s concentrate. Do not reuse them. Follow manufacturer’s instructions for cleaning/maintaining PPE. If no such instructions for washables, use detergent and hot water. Keep and wash PPE separately from other laundry.
